Strategic Direction
Cooper Standard has a clear vision for success. Discover how the global automotive supplier will achieve its growth goals by driving value through its culture, innovation and results. Click for more »



 



 
i³ Innovation Process
See how Cooper Standard is continually driving a culture of big ideas and big innovation with its i3 Process, a new initiative that understand passion and game-changing ideas can come from anyone – whether they’re within the company or from suppliers. Click for more »



 



 
Corporate Responsibility - Our Commitment
Cooper Standard is pleased to release its first Corporate Responsibility report which provides an overview of its commitment, while also highlighting its culture of engagement. Click for more »



 








 





 





 





