What Sets Us Apart
 
 










We are innovating in places you’d least expect it and accelerating game-changing advancements in material science to produce green solutions and automotive components that reduce weight, lower emissions, enhance design and improve vehicle performance for our customers. Our products and systems can be found on all major automaker platforms around the world.

Our roadmap and vision for future success is clearly defined in our Strategy. The first phase of our Profitable Growth Strategy began in 2013 and established a clear vision, set of values and strategy to achieve the Company’s goal to double in size. The second phase of our Strategy was announced in 2016 and refines the initial strategy to provide a path to further accelerate growth and more closely represent our culture.
Our Profitable Growth Strategy leverages Cooper Standard’s global scale and leading positions in our core product lines of Sealing Systems, Fuel and Brake Delivery Systems, Fluid Transfer Systems and Anti-Vibration Systems. As a result, Cooper Standard has met or exceeded our growth goals and is poised for a future of growth as a top global automotive supplier. Whether our customers need help solving a specific engineering challenge or developing systems for future vehicles, we’re able to meet their needs through our:





 

Integrated Solutions
Technology leadership, combined with broad product expertise and capabilities, enables us to find solutions to customer challenges.
Global Resources
We have design, engineering and manufacturing expertise and engineering resources in all major automotive markets, ensuring support of our customers throughout the world.
Operational Excellence
We are committed to driving sustained excellence in every aspect of our operations through the Cooper Standard Operating System, our customized set of global best practices designed for quality and lean initiatives, supply chain management and capacity optimization.
Our People
From our experienced management team to our expert engineers, manufacturing and professional staff, our employees continue to be one of our most important assets and the heart and soul of our Company and our success.

 
 
 



