Supplemental Information 1




Company Profile




■URLhttp://www.cooperstandard.com
■Address39550 Orchard Hill Place Drive, Novi, Michigan 48375, USA




Business Overview


			-The Company is a leading manufacturer of automotive systems and components across four different product segments: Sealing systems, fuel and brake delivery systems, fluid transfer systems, and anti-vibration systems.-According to the Company's research, the Company is the number 1 ranked global supplier for sealing systems, the number 2 ranked global supplier for fuel and brake delivery systems, the number 3 ranked supplier for fluid transfer systems, and the North American leading supplier for anti-vibration systems.-The Company is organized into four operating segments by region: North America, Europe, Asia Pacific, and South America.-A key aspect of the Company's growth strategy is expanding its sales and manufacturing operations, especially in China. Capital investments in China as well as the acquisition of shares in the Huayu-Cooper Standard Sealing Systems joint venture have lead to growth in the country. The Company's sales in China increased by 43.9% and 142.7% in the fiscal years ended December 31, 2014 and 2015, respectively, which exceeded the growth rate of any of the Company's other major markets. Competitors 


Sealing systems
Fuel and brake delivery products
Fluid transfer products
Anti-vibration systems


-Toyoda Gosei-Hutchinson-Henniges-Standard Profil

-TI Automotive-Sanoh-Martinrea-Usui-Maruyasu
-ContiTech-Hutchinson-Tristone-Hwaseung R&A-Teklas
-Trelleborg/Vibracoustic-Hutchinson-Sumitomo Riko-Bridgestone-ContiTech



