Headquartered in Tokyo, MarkLines is a Japanese company listed on the JASDAQ stock exchange. 
The MarkLines Automotive Industry Portal provides vehicle production and sales information, technology reports, part supplier insights for almost 50,000 suppliers, and much more for companies around the world. Additionally, MarkLines provides an online service for OEMs and suppliers to promote their products.
More than 2,100 automotive industry companies from all levels of the supply chain, including OEMs, parts makers, and material suppliers, are currently subscribed to MarkLines' service.




